<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2.1</NUMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Modeling Technology Assumptions</ENAMEX>
Scenarios A and B are based on <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the AEO2001</TIMEX> standard and advanced
