<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2.1.1</NUMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">Reference Case Scenario</ENAMEX>
The scenario A reference case assumes a "business-as-usual"
characterization of technology development and deployment. As
projected in <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">the AEO2001</TIMEX> assessment, the <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">nation</ENAMEX>'s economy is
