increase by <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">1.8%</NUMEX> <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">annually</TIMEX>. Further details are provided in Appendix
5.2.1.


<NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2.1.2</NUMEX>. <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Advanced Technology</ENAMEX> Scenario
Under the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">AEO</ENAMEX> <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">2001</TIMEX> advanced technology characterization,
