prior to the introduction of the caps; (<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">2</ENAMEX>) the varying levels of
demand for electricity over time, resulting in changes in the
overall mix of generation resources; and, (<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">3</ENAMEX>) the gradual reduction
